This paper is primarily focused on the security and management of IP addresses, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI) and distributed systems (cs.DC). The use of blockchain technology for this purpose also makes it relevant to the sub-category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation and evaluation of IPchain, which involves aspects of software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
